{"tid":2449857,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫苗接種︱蔡堅遭狙擊批「A字膊」：人命關天 從醫49年做不到無資料下拍心口","createTime":"2021-03-17T03:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:40:17.000Z","uid":130626,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e8fdb0d075c9057e3894d68726d42e6b813e0c1d","tid":2449857,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"衞生署將向私家醫生提供簡介疫苗接種指引，醫學會會長蔡堅昨日批評指引模糊及空泛，形容「少少敷衍式」，又質疑為何不暫時停止為60歲以上人士接種科興疫苗。有親建制報章專欄批評其言論為「A字膊」，質疑私家醫生拒絕承擔責任及欠專業精神。蔡堅今（17日）反駁指控，稱問清楚指引內容「是必須的，因為人命關天」，又指既然指引列明病情失控不宜打針，便應說明「達到那種水平才算失控」；如果只靠醫生自行判斷，只是「齋噏」。蔡又指，從醫49年，從沒接觸過武漢肺炎疫苗，如果要求他在沒證據及資料的情況下「拍心口」，他做不到。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/KTEUPP65ANHGHCF76DS2JHDKHY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FKTEUPP65ANHGHCF76DS2JHDKHY%2F&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixXB8Xc4SSRTU1%2BC3UxNwN9M%3D&h=13104941\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210317%2FKTEUPP65ANHGHCF76DS2JHDKHY%2F&h=ebfdf736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210317/KTEUPP65ANHGHCF76DS2JHDKHY/</a>"},{"pid":"d20b37d6c596e14386f27d0f1b6580c6262a1162","tid":2449857,"uid":184022,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T03:58:59.000Z","msg":"問清標準=推卸責任，有幾on9先講得出？"},{"pid":"2142ab81fe9c4e9fd0ed85e1f835b35e8b4437fb","tid":2449857,"uid":33373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:03:32.000Z","msg":"如果只靠醫生自行判斷，只是「齋噏」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實"},{"pid":"4fa2c0861a9bb094b73419250483f198c12ac88e","tid":2449857,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T04:03:56.000Z","msg":"醫德 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f82f397e7c19aecac5ffd39471ea83c989f0d5b","tid":2449857,"uid":325346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T0